{"tid":1107056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綜緩等雙糧最快預算案通過後一個月發放","createTime":"2019-04-15T03:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T04:37:48.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a74e768e8d05a353ab8d81edbcb6c3202d81de41","tid":1107056,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"《財政預算案》提出向領取綜援、生果金、長者生活津貼、傷殘津貼、低收入在職家庭津貼和鼓勵就業交通津貼人士，發放雙糧，勞工及福利局副局長徐英偉表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>受惠人最快可以在立法會通過預算案後一個月領取額外金額</strong></span>，涉及總開支約40億元。<br />\n<br />\n徐英偉於立法會福利事務委員會續指，向每名有經濟需要學生發放2500元的津貼，會在今年第三季陸續發放，涉及9億元。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會陸頌雄指庫房水浸，政府應該將學生的一次過津貼受惠範圍，擴展至所有學生，徐英偉回應指，政府目標是盡量幫助有需要人士，因此安排與往年一樣，未有涵蓋所有學生。"},{"pid":"84ac52b5634f4cd2f5573a2ad220113594505efa","tid":1107056,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"4000 係上年預算案仲未收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72832bcd4af6b8f868eb7d624ca21f473dbd407f","tid":1107056,"uid":247924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cac2811338a8f30d150730430a0b9f79f279e5b","tid":1107056,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d9d947eadc470b274da1905fe20ba7bd29645b3","tid":1107056,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"綜援撚連表都唔洗填屌你老母"},{"pid":"c2bcdba97d695b3149205ecb40451c9caa766f98","tid":1107056,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"又益大陸狗"},{"pid":"6d7001a5e3b9023dffdd8b8bab7a228e4940cb2a","tid":1107056,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"0489cade430e9fafd94aea1ac2d3ebb1310d0edb","tid":1107056,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\